{"type": "article", "id": 3598, "title": "Courage and Liberty联名系列腕表", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-17T08:01:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232625AVwnKYEJ9M2i7ufk.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在去年合作成功的基础之上，法国腕表品牌 LIP 今年再度携手法国男装时尚品牌 Commune de Paris ，推出了全新联名系列「\r\n\t</p>\n<p>\r\n\t\tCourage and Liberty<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">」。这一次的合作双方选择了 LIP 腕表的两个经典款 Panorami 与 Himalaya 作为蓝本进行重新设计，最新推出的 4 个版本表盘的细节均做了调整，此外，每一款表盘还配有相应的尼龙编织的表带，配色的选择上更显活泼。「Commune de Paris」系列将于 12 月初登陆 LIP 线上商店，Panorami 款定价 179 欧元，Panorami 款定价 199 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.lip.fr/en/creators/special_editions/commune_de_paris_1871/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</span>\r\n\t</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232623uoErgGRFO8I75phf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1421875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052326236cWyRsVKar95PlBz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1421875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232624gxmbzBlHULf9hwJN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232624St2d7paPBgyis3Oo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.759375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}